  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ebola Community Action Platform (E-CAP)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To respond to the Ebola virus disease epidemic in Liberia, Mercy Corps will partner with Population Services International to leverage community-based networks and health messaging to contribute to the Ebola social mobilization strategy in Liberia.  E-CAP will coordinate with partners on the ground to activate community task forces. The program will invest in training and materials, nationwide digital outreach and mass media communications to enhance awareness and uptake of behaviors which reduce the transmission of the Ebola virus disease.</narrative>
  </description>
